{"tid":448396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[養兒投資失利] 菜刀狂斬熟睡父母　被捕逆子：我好憎我老竇","createTime":"2017-10-26T07:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T08:43:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e69ea28f67c10305a39af145aa9f92f2674685","tid":448396,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"上水發生倫常血案，男子涉嫌斬傷熟睡父母，他被捕後仍喃喃自語：「我好憎我老竇」。慘案現場清河邨清顯樓10樓一單位，住有一家3口，包括一對夫婦及其兒子。今晨6時許，53歲姓林戶主正在睡覺，突遭人用菜刀狂斬，以致頭中4刀、頸中1刀，以及臉部亦有刀傷，血流披面，他負創跑去屋外，沿走廊及樓梯逃至大廈大堂向保安員求助。其42歲姓葉妻子驚見發生血案，立即報警。期間兒子更持刀追出屋外，葉婦連忙尾隨制止，母子在走廊拉扯，糾纏間，她耳朵被鎅傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171026/bkn-20171026064724945-1026_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171026%2Fbkn-20171026064724945-1026_00822_001.html&d=4IF1C649KVaN%2BhE9NTL1iQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f28ac3fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171026/bkn-20171026064724945-1026_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c63a28d351cba366f7e363e4bac4fe59371e8a81","tid":448396,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"養兒防老苦主大聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d9ca003f2a46130f5a19f740a7526df014c2e2","tid":448396,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"老豆養到佢咁大都唔識感恩"},{"pid":"7d050e4a47ab22b2b955a42dbb16eeff0196f138","tid":448396,"uid":38523,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆養到佢咁大都唔識感恩</blockquote><br />\n你老母養你咁大咪又係要做支那五毛狗"},{"pid":"0cb932e78974f93602d4701a960bc461f85b0e9e","tid":448396,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"點解妓者咁快可以斷定係「逆子」<br />\n<br />\n唔比係老豆仆街既？"},{"pid":"dfbca1fe4d655e9dc0b76fd4dfb0904e4d41c8de","tid":448396,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"警方交代案情，並且檢走染血枕頭、床單及菜刀等證物。大埔警區刑事總督察鄭則恒指，疑犯中四輟學，從事裝修工，兩年前開始接受精神科治療，父親為職業司機，母親為售貨員，父子經常為家中瑣事嘈交，2、3日前亦曾大吵一場。事發時，有人到廚房飲水後，突然狂性大發，取來12吋長菜刀向在客廳熟睡的父親連環揮刀狂斬，"},{"pid":"38732f3fedb66ce7f8dd3506c65929b229bd9d8c","tid":448396,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解妓者咁快可以斷定係「逆子」<br />\n<br />\n唔比係老豆仆街既？</blockquote><br />\n呢度香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066498c16f47818bf694a7c75ec87d6f0ee885ec","tid":448396,"uid":132524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解妓者咁快可以斷定係「逆子」<br />\n<br />\n唔比係老豆仆街既？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6eb91dc5cd31356df2131789625f3e979b1e47","tid":448396,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬算唔算失利個案"},{"pid":"124074eb2f16e349a87130afbaf5c2bf862f2d8f","tid":448396,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"老貓，你點睇你父母"},{"pid":"c9b84f681545841d8eab4a85d23ff1f6ee68a552","tid":448396,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:40:23.000Z","msg":"其他失利都有返工<br />\n樓豬直頭唔返了"},{"pid":"7ded5155be55e3997f8c01132c57999c59528fad","tid":448396,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬算唔算失利個案</blockquote><br />\n我想知佢父母點睇佢"},{"pid":"99676316dedc9a6c101680f1796e504ef39a80aa","tid":448396,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬算唔算失利個案</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7feef2f87166d859